{"lastModified":1764333616443,"uri":"c::7580644256::vessel::d5cc25f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor","Power Catamaran"],"description":"Summer/Winter Operating Area: Mediterranean/Greece\n\nCHARTER IN GREECE THIS SUMMER ABOARD SKYLARK\n\nExperience the ultimate luxury vacation on board SKYLARK, a 70′ (21.34m) Catamaran built by the renowned Sunreef Yachts. With unparalleled 360º ocean views, SKYLARK is the ideal vessel for cruising the stunning Mediterranean waters. Whether you’re looking for a relaxing getaway or an adventure-filled vacation, this yacht offers world-class service and unforgettable experiences.","blueprint":{"name":"SKYLARK","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc25f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::24e20fa0-eae5-11ef-a543-230d0347a9f4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc25f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::24f178f0-eae5-11ef-b095-83f86a5233b0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7580644256::vessel::d5cc25f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::678fbba0-ed0f-11ef-a7ee-eb7c5804f57d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc25f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::24f06780-eae5-11ef-b095-83f86a5233b0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc25f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::24e480a0-eae5-11ef-a543-230d0347a9f4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc25f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::24e0d720-eae5-11ef-a543-230d0347a9f4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc25f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::24e19a70-eae5-11ef-a543-230d0347a9f4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc25f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::24e2fa00-eae5-11ef-a543-230d0347a9f4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc25f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::24e34820-eae5-11ef-a543-230d0347a9f4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc25f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::24e60741-eae5-11ef-a543-230d0347a9f4/{imageV